<h1>Call to Adventure!</h1>
<p>
  The land needs heroes: brave warriors from near and far, ready for an epic quest. Their mission:
  to come to <strong>The Green</strong> in <strong>Sutton</strong> on <strong>Saturday 19 August 2023</strong>
  for a summer garden party set to amuse both young and old. Will you answer the call?
</p>
<hr>
<h2>You're Invited!</h2>
<p>
  To view your invitation, speak your secret magic word:
</p>
<%= form_tag "/login", method: :post, class: 'one-line-form' do %>
  <input type="text" name="code" placeholder="speak friend and enter" required autofocus>
  <input type="submit" value="Log in">
<% end %>
<hr>
<h3>Don't know your magic word?</h3>
<p>
  Fear not! Enter your email address or phone number below, and we'll send a spell of recall to your
  inbox or your mobile:
</p>
<%= form_tag "/remind", method: :post, class: 'one-line-form' do %>
  <input type="text" name="contact" placeholder="phone / email" required>
  <input type="submit" value="Remind me">
<% end %>
